text: URZ may refer to: * IATA airport code for Uruzgan Airport, in Khas Uruzgan, Afghanistan, from the List of airports by IATA code: U * URZ AP (Univerzální Ruční Zbraň Automatická Puška), an assault rifle of Czechoslovak origin * "urz", ISO 639-3 language code of the language of the Uru-Eu-Wau-Wau people ==See also== * Brime de Urz, a municipality located in the province of Zamora, Castile and León, Spain * Quintanilla de Urz, a municipality located in the province of Zamora, Castile and León, Spain
title: URZ
